title: Pierre Feidt
text: Pierre Feidt (born 13 January 1904, date of death unknown) was a Luxembourgian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201924%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20middleweight">men's middleweight</a> event at the <a href="1924%20Summer%20Olympics">1924 Summer Olympics</a>.
